channel.name: How to diagnose "Can not reach the server - please reload the page"

messages.content:
I created a UI that is constantly updating a global webpage. Whenever I close the browser and reopen it to try and load the updating page it gives me the error of "Can not reach the server - please reload the page". If I click reload it doesnt update the page but if I click on one of the buttons the UI comes to life and I can see It updating. 

How would I got about trying to fix this or diagnosing what in my code is causing this problem?

Best,
W
